      "rationale": "Three-mesh GCI study performed: coarse (2.1M cells), medium (5.8M cells), fine (14.2M cells). GCI for NIH on fine mesh: 4.7%; GCI for pressure head: 2.8%. Observed order of convergence p=1.87 (theoretical p=2 for second-order scheme). Fine mesh selected for all production runs. Exceeds MRL 2 requirement by achieving formal Richardson extrapolation with GCI quantification.",
