      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "Experimental validation data collected under controlled laboratory conditions matching CPB operating envelope: flow rates 3–6 L/min, rotational speeds 2000–3500 RPM, blood analog fluid (glycerol-water 36% by mass, viscosity 3.5 cP at 37°C). Temperature maintained at 37±0.5°C. Instrumentation calibrated per ISO 17511. Test conditions documented in laboratory notebook LN-2023-047.",
