        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "QoI relevance acceptance criteria for MRL 2",
        "description": "QoIs must be directly linked to the clinical or engineering decision. Traceability from model output to decision criterion must be documented. Gradation 2 requires explicit mapping of QoIs to acceptance criteria in the COU."
