      "rationale": "Validation activities conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry — the same geometry class as the device under assessment. Operating conditions in validation experiments span the full CPB operating envelope defined in the COU. Blood analog fluid properties match those used in predicate device hemolysis testing per ISO 10993-4 guidance. Validation-to-COU relevance gap is minimal.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
