        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Validation activity relevance acceptance criteria for MRL 2",
        "description": "Validation experiments must be conducted on a geometry and under conditions sufficiently similar to the COU. Any gaps between validation scenario and COU must be documented and assessed for impact. Gradation 2 requires documented similarity argument."
