      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Test sample characterization (geometric fidelity of physical test article relative to nominal CAD, material properties of test pump components) is scoped out at MRL 2. The FDA generic pump geometry is a reference artifact with published dimensional tolerances; deviations from nominal are within ±0.1 mm per FDA benchmark documentation. Formal geometric metrology of test samples is reserved for MRL 3."
